      <context>
         <p>You must create a mapping for the External Id field prior to initiating an object sync. After you have completed the <xref href="../mapping-fields_143887215_143887215/143887215.xml"
                  format="dita">initial mapping</xref>, perform the following tasks in order:</p>
      </context>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Create a custom field named "External Id" with field type String/Text in both the <uicontrol>source and destination system</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Create a mapping field record named "Id" for the object to be synced, using the API names specified in the previous step.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
